'''World Skate''' is the governing body of [[roller sports]]. It was created by the merging of the [[Fédération Internationale de Roller Sports]] and the [[International Skateboarding Federation]] in September of 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.shop-eat-surf.com/content/olympic-announcement-precedes-first-park-terrain-skateboarding-world-championships|title=Olympic Announcement Precedes First Park Terrain Skateboarding World Championships|first=Magda Liszewska|last=Hernandez|date=9 August 2016|publisher=}}</ref>

